<NEW>

LORD ELDER was watching the screen as NIGHTSHIFT worked."I have no
idea why the Predacons do what they do." He said. "Plus we don't know
if they are still cooperating or not."

ELDER grunted, "They could be peacemakers or they could have turned on
Leo Prime. We won't know until we can restore communications, and I
think that the satellite might have enough power to punch through the
interference, or at least analyze it."

Then ELDER saw the numbers for CHEETOR appear on NIGHTSHIFT's screen.
He glanced at LEGACY, PERCEPTOR and WINDLORD hoping one of themn had
an answer for why a missing MAXIMAL's clearance code would be part of
a sabotage attempt against CRYONOSIS.

(TAG)

- Preston
